data.meta_description: 466 likes, 34 comments - davidhumekennerly on November 18, 2021: "The horror. 43 years ago today over 900 people died in a murder/suicide nightmare at Jonestown in #Guyana —It was the worst thing i’ve ever photographed. This cultish behavior is extreme, but could happen again upon the order of another demented leader. @jackiespeier was there working for Rep. Leo Ryan who was murdered. She was shot 5 times, but survived. #jonestown #jimjones @totallyeffnlost".
